2006-06-15 21:34  kevinkofler

	* mainform.ui, mainform.ui.h: Improve Auto Blocks:
	  * Hook Enter/Return key.
	  * Only create a block immediately if { is on its own in a line,
	  otherwise wait for Enter/Return to be pressed. This prevents
	  annoying the user while typing things like strings.  (The Windows
	  IDE also works like that.)

