	  buttons were placed.  All radio buttons are now in button groups so
	  that they will be mutually exclusive.  Also set buttonClose to send
	  accept(), even though it doesn't really matter what ProgramOptions
	  sends when it closes. (unless for some reason we decided to make a
	  menu item in the MainForm for this dialog).

